Installation
================================================================================
1) cd into webroot
2) git clone git://github.com/infinitas/infinitas.git infinitas/
3) cd infinitas/

4) If you would like the extra plugins (recomended)
	4a) git submodule init
	4b) git submodule update

5) make config/ tmp/ writeable for the installation
6) create a db (remember the name and login details for just now)
7) visit the corresponding url to where you cloned it to (http://localhost/infinitas/ maybe)
8) Follow the instructions
9) pat yourself on the back